### 1. GET Published Events Sorted by Start Date
GET http://localhost:4004/api/events/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate asc

### 2. GET Events Filtered by Type "Workshop"
GET http://localhost:4004/api/events/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'

### 3. GET All Registrations for a Specific Event
GET http://localhost:4004/api/events/Registrations?$filter=event_ID eq 'aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa'

### 4. POST a New Registration
POST http://localhost:4004/api/events/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
"event_ID": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
"attendeeName": "Vayom Tyagi",
"attendeeEmail": "[vayom.tyagi@gmail.com](mailto:vayom.tyagi@gmail.com)",
"attendeePhone": "9876543210",
"company": "GLA University",
"ticketType": "VIP",
"registrationDate": "2026-06-01T10:00:00Z",
"amountPaid": 999.00,
"paymentId": "PAY99999"
}

### 5. GET Speakers Sorted by Rating Descending
GET http://localhost:4004/api/events/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### 6. GET Events with Available Seats
GET http://localhost:4004/api/events/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### 7. PATCH Event Status from Draft to Published
PATCH http://localhost:4004/api/events/Events('cccccccc-cccc-cccc-cccc-cccccccccccc')
Content-Type: application/json

{
"status": "Published"
}

### 8. POST Feedback for an Event
POST http://localhost:4004/api/events/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
"event_ID": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
"attendeeEmail": "[vayom.tyagi@gmail.com](mailto:vayom.tyagi@gmail.com)",
"overallRating": 5,
"contentRating": 5,
"venueRating": 4,
"speakerRating": 5,
"comment": "Excellent workshop with practical examples.",
"submittedAt": "2026-07-10T18:00:00Z"
}
